{"tid":316901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國女遊客峇里島旅遊染怪病昏迷","createTime":"2017-07-11T05:33:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T05:38:39.000Z","uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3b15096f311312ebfd9a90606f2f9ebd864ab04d","tid":316901,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:33:14.000Z","msg":"中國女遊客峇里島旅遊染怪病昏迷<br />\n<br />\n一名中國女遊客日前在印尼峇里島旅遊時，突發腦部疾病被送往當地醫院，至今未脫離生命危險。<br />\n<br />\n7月初，33歲的中國女子楊婷與朋友一起去峇里島旅行，5日早上，原本準備和朋友出去玩的楊婷有點發燒。朋友隨後發現楊婷開始神志不清，找到旅行社領隊，將楊婷送往當地醫院。轉了3次院，楊婷才住進當地一家國際醫院的深切治療部檢查治療。醫生說，楊婷病情嚴重。旅行社通知楊婷母親，讓她立刻飛往峇里島。<br />\n<br />\n楊婷家人趕到峇里島後發現，楊婷躺在床上昏迷不醒，身體輕輕動一下，全身就會不停抽搐。醫生檢查發現，楊婷發病是因為腦部感染了病毒，具體是什麼病毒，至今沒有查出來。因為沒有查出病因，醫生只能對楊婷進行保守治療。醫生說，長期抽搐會造成腦損傷。<br />\n<br />\n7月9日，楊婷肺部感染，病情進一步惡化，醫生建議楊婷家人帶她回國治療。由於楊婷病情嚴重，只能包機回國。而包機費用需要80萬元人民幣，家人準備賣房救她。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1605307/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A5%B3%E9%81%8A%E5%AE%A2%E5%B3%87%E9%87%8C%E5%B3%B6%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A%E6%9F%93%E6%80%AA%E7%97%85%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1605307%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E9%2581%258A%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%25B3%2587%25E9%2587%258C%25E5%25B3%25B6%25E6%2597%2585%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%259F%2593%25E6%2580%25AA%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%2598%258F%25E8%25BF%25B7&d=RWfcpYAj8BCAA7VXPsDiDARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=b9a55b8d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1605307/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A5%B3%E9%81%8A%E5%AE%A2%E5%B3%87%E9%87%8C%E5%B3%B6%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A%E6%9F%93%E6%80%AA%E7%97%85%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B7</a>"},{"pid":"d2f8ee7425ae9b1e17d6ef2563e74c519e28e1e2","tid":316901,"uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:35:04.000Z","msg":"旅遊保險唔包?定冇買?"},{"pid":"721011fbfe2394c526c1ddb3ec80abdef78cabc7","tid":316901,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:35:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1585d86976be320e18e2f2393557e3bb4ae50ca6","tid":316901,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:35:30.000Z","msg":"失去祖國煙霧力場保護就死鳩左"},{"pid":"6600cef7fd6e00e9790febd3e0998502cb29ddf9","tid":316901,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:36:06.000Z","msg":"MIC WFC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85972330f652b19258340c710d6d02e55c922350","tid":316901,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:38:39.000Z","msg":"日本腦炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}